<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Uso de HTTPS requerido</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>HTTPS requerido</h1>
    <p>Esta página no permite el uso de HTTP.</p>
    <p>Por favor, <a href="https://@Context.Request.Host@Context.Request.Path">vuelve a cargar usando HTTPS</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>